headline: Thermo Fisher Scientific Launches the Thermo Scientific Hypulse Surface Analysis System to Accelerate the Understanding of Material Surfaces
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., September 22, 2025--Thermo Fisher Scientific, the world leader in serving science, has introduced the Thermo Scientific™ Hypulse™ Surface Analysis System. This innovative surface analysis instrument represents a leap forward in accurate X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy (XPS) depth-profiling, which is critical for materials scientists around the world.
